<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>RLST 23150.  Capitalism and Doing Good?  100 Units.</strong></p><p class="courseblockdesc">
This class asks the question: is it possible to believe in capitalism (i.e., the private ownership of wealth) and do good for society? Restated, are there values that can accompany capital accumulation for positive social impact on people and the environment?</p><p class="courseblockdetail">
