<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>RLST 28101.  Iblis: Muslim Perspectives on the Devil.  100 Units.</strong></p><p class="courseblockdesc">
This course examines a range of Muslim perspectives on the Devil. Is Iblis a personification of evil, an archetype of arrogant rebellion against divine command, a perfect monotheist and tragic lover of God, or an ally of humankind and teacher of freedom and creativity? Our readings will include selections from the Qur'an and hadith, Sufi poetry, modern political and theological writing, and others.</p><p class="courseblockdetail">
